EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   12 THRU 18 MAY WITHIN 15 MILES OF 57-25.5N 008-06.5W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 947/12(57).
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 181900Z MAY.
